<D>__{holy shit.}
<A>__{then a headline which reads: "head maternity nurse questioned on infant deaths" next page: "miss wilkes released." next page: "three more infants die." next page, at last: "dragon lady arrested." then a photo: the front page of the rocky mountain gazette. annie on the courthouse steps. "dragon lady claims innocence," under which there is a statement by annie wilkes. paul turns quickly to the next page and a very large headline: "dragon lady found not guilty" paul just sits there, shaking his head in bewilderment.}
